The engineering society sponsors a resume review table near the stage, and tech companies display demo screens showing their latest apps. Consulting firms stack glossy case study booklets on high tables, and healthcare providers showcase community outreach photos. Workshops on networking etiquette begin in the adjoining classroom, and an alumni panel discusses how to prepare for technical interviews. In the midst of this, human resources teams jot notes on tablets while students introduce themselves, and a whiteboard lists employers who are scheduling same-day interviews. Additionally, students compare swag items like water bottles and phone chargers.

As the day winds down, interview sign-up sheets fill with names, and human resources teams jot notes on tablets while students introduce themselves. Meanwhile, friends decompress on the quad, comparing which companies responded warmly, and international students queue for advice on visa sponsorship requirements. Alumni volunteers share quick pep talks near the coffee station, and a data science company showcases a live dashboard of fair attendance.
